    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081840/extras/35ca597184bd599dad11122d6836f91c.avif?t=1759792197\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081840/extras_big/35ca597184bd599dad11122d6836f91c.avif?t=1759792197 width=800 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Ouro Kronii, the Warden of Time. Your desire to become the strongest being in the universe led to the creation of the Chrono Gear, an artifact with the power to preserve timelines. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But where power lies, evil will seek to control it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fierce battle against the demonic Alter Laplus has shattered the Chrono Gear, scattering its Golden Gears across the stars. As Kronii, you must fight against the darkness that shattered your universe, find the Golden Gears, and repair the space-time continuum. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Chrono Gear: Warden of Time</i> is a retro 2D action game that mixes speedy platforming and sword combat with explorable hub areas and a dramatic story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081840/extras/5de9cdc7b83ba34bbc6fb5d9ebbccd8a.avif?t=1759792197\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081840/extras_big/5de9cdc7b83ba34bbc6fb5d9ebbccd8a.avif?t=1759792197 width=800 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Control the flow of time with Kronii's special abilities, using Haste to accelerate time and Stasis to slow down time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speed your way through missions to achieve the fastest time records or explore for hidden collectibles; The game caters to either play style!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Relax in central hub areas that connect you to each destination in your journey and become increasingly populated with hololive talents and fans as you make progress in the story </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jam out to a pulse pounding soundtrack with over 75 pieces of collectible music, including remixes of popular hololive originals</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081840/extras/3d6db4b8a8cf6d05f3ca0c9c82fe4785.avif?t=1759792197\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081840/extras_big/3d6db4b8a8cf6d05f3ca0c9c82fe4785.avif?t=1759792197 width=800 height=326 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is published under CCMC Corp(※1)'s Indie game brand &quot;holo Indie&quot;.(※2)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is allowed to be monetized under the examination and terms of &quot;holo Indie&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please note that any monetized derivative work games that include Cover Corp.'s content outside of holo Indie is not covered by these terms and is not allowed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※1. About CCMC Corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CCMC Corp. is entrusted with website management (ex: Steam) including, examination, publishing and other necessary tasks by Cover Corp.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※2. About &quot;holo Indie&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >holo Indie's objective is to cooperate with hololive production fans and creators.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is a game brand that offers &quot;Game Creator Support Program&quot; for the derivative work games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For more details about &quot;holo Indie&quot;, Please refer to the Cover Corp.'s &quot;Derivative work guidelines&quot;.</p>",
